; UTILITY: supersaw — four detuned saws around a 1V/oct note; `detune` breathes the spread.
; (:cents on the saw builds the phasor itself, so each voice is just one saw. The saw shape is
; Loupe's DPW oscillator, which we took from Chris Johnson's code — see the `shape` node.)
(def supersaw (fn (:note :detune)
  (mix (mix (saw note :cents (add vmid detune))
            (saw note :cents (sub vmid detune)))
       (mix (saw note :cents (add vmid (div detune 3)))
            (saw note :cents (sub vmid (div detune 3)))))))
